Target thickness corresponded to the energy loss of

Isotope targets were prepared directly in the
electromagnetic separator by beating of the 36Ar ions
into beryllium backings. Argon of natural isotopic
composition was used for target preparation. Targets
manufactured from unenriched gas contained
approximately 25% of 40Ar.
